 Docker service, environment variable, system property, or extra Maven dependency required.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No environment or system-property setup is required. The observed javac failure is an API/package change: org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator.Iterables is no longer in janino 3.1.0; the related class is in org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator.Iterables via the already-transitive commons-compiler dependency. Prefer covering public Janino APIs such as SimpleCompiler, ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, and CompilerFactory rather than relying on removed internal utility packages.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Adding an explicit org.codehaus.janino:commons-compiler dependency is redundant for normal Gradle/Maven usage because janino 3.1.0 already declares it as a regular dependency.\",\n    \"Janino has an optional/provided Ant integration dependency; do not test AntCompilerAdapter unless the workflow intentionally adds Ant, because it is not needed for meaningful core Janino coverage.\",\n    \"Native Image may still expose Janino dynamic class-loading limitations, so local Gradle and native-image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a512b1ba408c913016a41fac15d2081948169550e379a5cef\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 895, "output": 1252, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24163, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782708914476, "responseId": "resp_0a512b1ba408c913016a41fab2ee24819485cc5ba6926ca070"}, "toolResults": []}
